                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;del&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2430&quot; title=&quot;Migration tool for DNE&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2430&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2430&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/del&gt; is not present on 2.5.x esp the change &quot;&lt;del&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2430&quot; title=&quot;Migration tool for DNE&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2430&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2430&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/del&gt; mdd: add lfs mv to migrate inode.&quot; so for MDS version less than 2.6.57 this test needs to be SKIPPed otherwise the test would fail with&lt;/p&gt;
